        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "In the morning we woke to window ledges heaped white, and snowflakes falling so whirling thick that it was impossible to see ten feet ahead.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
