        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "Right away!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "\"You are no better than murderers!\" he cried.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000006_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000006_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "\"Shooting down your Russian brothers on the streets!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000010_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000010_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "The captain shouted at the top of his voice.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "You should remain neutral!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000010_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000010_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "Who are you to destroy the legal Government?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000010_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000010_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "A German-\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000011_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000011_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "\"Who are you?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000012_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000012_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "\"All right!\" said he.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000012_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000012_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "\"You call yourselves the people of Russia.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000012_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000012_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "Wait until the peasants-\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "\"Yes,\" they cried, \"wait until the peasants speak.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000013_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000013_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "Aren't they workingmen like ourselves?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000014_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000014_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "While the peasants had been politically backward, still they had their own peculiar ideas, and they constituted more than eighty per cent of the people of Russia.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "He must study the aspects of the agrarian problem in the province.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000019_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000019_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "Who administers the confiscated land-the former proprietor, or the Land Committees?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000020_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000020_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "What has been done with the agricultural machinery and with the farm animals?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000021_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000021_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "Has the ground cultivated by the peasants been augmented?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000022_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000022_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "How much and in what respect does the amount of land now under cultivation differ from the amount fixed by the Government as an average minimum?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000025_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000025_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "It is desirable that agricultural properties well appointed and well organised should be administered by Soviets composed of the regular employees of those properties, under the direction of competent agricultural scientists.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "The great hall was jammed with people and shaken with continual clamour; deep, stubborn bitterness divided the delegates into angry groups.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000029_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000029_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "The galleries were thronged with workers-who, in Russia, still remember their peasant origin....",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000031_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000031_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "Whereupon the old Executive Committee left the hall....",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000035_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000035_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "We don't recognise your Government!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000036_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000036_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "Finally, except for the right side of the hall, the demonstration wore itself out somewhat.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000038_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000038_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "\"However,\" he went on, in an unmoved voice, \"nobody will deny that the present Government of Russia has been formed by the Bolshevik party-\" he had to wait a moment, \"so that for all purposes it is the same thing....\" Here the right benches broke into deafening clamour, but the centre and left were curious, and compelled silence.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000039_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000039_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "Lenin's argument was simple.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000039_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000039_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "Are you going to allow the ranks of the proletariat to be divided?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000041_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000041_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "Anybody who attempts to destroy the Soviets is guilty of an anti democratic and counter revolutionary act.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000042_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000042_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "Only two months before considered an extreme revolutionist, and very popular with the peasants, he was now called to check the dangerous drift of the Congress toward the Left.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000043_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000043_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "His first act was to bitterly rebuke the Executive Committee for leaving the Congress.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000044_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000044_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "\"Comrades!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000045_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000045_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "Cries, \"Down with the Bolsheviki!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000046_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000046_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "Where does such an accusation come from?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000046_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000046_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "Show me the source!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000049_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000049_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "After a brief conversation I left-and that's all! Let any one present make such an accusation!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000052_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000052_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "Meanwhile, the question of the status of the Executive Committee was agitating all minds.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000052_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000052_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "By declaring the assembly \"Extraordinary Conference,\" it had been planned to block the reelection of the Executive Committee.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000052_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000052_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "But this worked both ways; the Left Socialist Revolutionists decided that if the Congress had no power over the Executive Committee, then the Executive Committee had no power over the Congress.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000054_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000054_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "On the twenty seventh occurred the debate on the Land question, which revealed the differences between the agrarian programme of the Bolsheviki and the Left Socialist Revolutionaries.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000055_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000055_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "The peasants understood the exact meaning of the Revolution-they tried to turn words into action....",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000056_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000056_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "\"The recent events,\" said the orator, \"do not indicate a simple riot, or a 'Bolshevik adventure,' but on the contrary, a real popular rising, which has been greeted with sympathy by the whole country....",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000057_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000057_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "From the first days, the Bolsheviki declared that the peasants should take over the land 'by revolutionary mass action.' This is nothing but anarchy; the land can be taken over in an organised manner....",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000058_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000058_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "\"The Land decree of the Congress of Soviets is identical in its fundamentals with the decisions of the first Peasants' Congress.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000059_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000059_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "However, no harm has been done by that; for the Land Committees are paying no attention to the Soviet decrees, but are putting into operation their own practical decisions-decisions based on the will of the vast majority of the peasants....",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000060_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000060_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "But will the Constituent Assembly desire to do the will of the Russian peasants?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000060_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000060_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "Of that we cannot be sure....",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000060_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000060_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "The Constituent Assembly will not dare to break with the will of the people....\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000061_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000061_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "Followed him Lenin, listened to now with absorbing intensity.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000061_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000061_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "\"At this moment we are not only trying to solve the Land question, but the question of Social Revolution-not only here in Russia, but all over the world.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000063_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000063_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "The Socialist political party-this is the vanguard of the working class; it must not allow itself to be halted by the lack of education of the mass average, but it must lead the masses, using the Soviets as organs of revolutionary initiative....",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000064_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000064_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "If Compromise continues, the Revolution disappears.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000065_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000065_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "\"We Bolsheviki have not changed our Land programme; we have not given up the abolition of private property in the land, and we do not intend to do so.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000066_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000066_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "\"We invite the Left Socialist Revolutionaries to enter that coalition, insisting, however, that they cease looking backward, and that they break with the 'conciliators' of their party....",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000067_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000067_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "\"As far as the Constituent Assembly is concerned, it is true, as the preceding speaker has said, that the work of the Constituent will depend on the revolutionary determination of the masses.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000067_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000067_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "I say, 'Count on that revolutionary determination, but don't forget your gun!'\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000072_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000072_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "For these reasons the Peasants' Congress sustains entirely the Revolution of november seventh... as a social revolution, and expresses its unalterable will to put into operation, with whatever modifications are necessary, but without any hesitation, the social transformation of the Russian Republic.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000073_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000073_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "From now on, in the Russian Republic, all the organisation and administration of the State, from top to bottom, must rest on that union.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000074_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000074_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "The reactionaries of the Executive Committee no longer dared openly to appear.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000074_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000074_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "He was invited to sit on the platform....",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000075_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000075_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "It seemed to me as if the Congress were hopelessly deadlocked.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000077_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000077_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "The Dumas and Zemstvos were dropped.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000077_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000077_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "Lenin and Trotzky remained in the Government, and the Military Revolutionary Committee continued to function.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000078_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000078_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "The old Executive Committee had withdrawn, and was holding a rump convention of its own in another room of the same building, made up of bolting delegates and representatives of the Army Committees.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000079_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000079_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "He knew that an agreement with the Bolsheviki was being discussed, but he did not know that it had been concluded.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000080_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000080_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "He spoke to the rump convention.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000080_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000080_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "Now people accuse Kerensky; they forget that he was raised to power, not only by the Soviets, but also by the popular masses....",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000081_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000081_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "The savages set up gods to which they pray, and which they punish if one of their prayers is not answered....",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000081_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000081_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "That is what is happening at this moment.... Yesterday Kerensky; to day Lenin and Trotzky; another to morrow....",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000082_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000082_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "\"We have proposed to both Kerensky and the Bolsheviki to retire from the power.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000083_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000083_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "\"If the Bolsheviki succeed, or if they fail, the fate of Russia will not be changed.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000083_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/6938/70848/6938_70848_000083_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "The Russian villages understand perfectly what they want, and they are now carrying out their own measures....",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-6938_70848_000086_000000",
