        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-6938",
        "content": "Then Boris Reinstein, delegate of the American Socialist Labor Party: \"The day of the union of the Congress of Peasants and the Soviets of Workers' and Soldiers' Deputies is one of the great days of the Revolution.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
